{"tid":1481562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈狗係任屌既","createTime":"2019-08-17T18:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T22:02:55.000Z","uid":92908,"like":708,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"4306cd76366956ab4234f0a6f738d127cc87df54","tid":1481562,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:15:38.000Z","msg":"平時係街度見到狗都會屌，好多時都唔敢望我，眼神閃閃縮縮<br />\n岩岩係屋企樓下大門，撚完2隻狗3隻藍屍廢老<br />\n有兩隻狗<br />\n唔知處理緊d咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗1 - pc 49159 年紀較大 一柴 狗公<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗2 - pc 25968 年紀較輕 冇柴 狗公<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對兩隻狗大叫：「咪係度搞事呀黑警！」然後繼續行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：「你講咩呀，咪走呀。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跑過黎，用手捉我膊頭，然後查我身份證<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />照比然後話：「我番緊屋企，要查快d」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />接身份證，跟手後面有3個廢老想郁手打我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一手拎住我身份證，一手頂住藍絲<br />\n（好似前線想捉住打人藍絲，但又比和理非㩒住咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就笑住望3個廢老<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「你幾多歲呀細路」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「你想知咪睇我身份證囉，反正係你師姐手上」（當時真係唔小心講錯師姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「你係唔係住呢度」指住我大堂門口<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「係」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「證明比我睇呀」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用八達通開門「嗱，開左，你可以開下度門架」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係去開一開門跟住又閂番<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真聽話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小狗二號好不容易擺平藍屍終於行番過黎我同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小狗一號個邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「依家我地要ckeck你袋」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「冇問題，check lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇左我個袋兩眼<br />\n然後我袋當然冇咩特別野喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「你係香港市民，所以受我地香港警察保護」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「咁又唔見你去元朗保護香港市民」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開始講廢話「我地唔係個區做野既，所以唔到我地管，嗱，你對頭先我地作出挑釁，有權告你xxxxx」（知道佢9up，自動過濾左）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「冇我見近排有好多人冒警，所以懷疑你地冒警姐，不過見到兩位呀sir人又nice，又有冧巴，我依家好放心」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「冇冧巴既係唔同部門，我地就係黎呢度處理嘈音投訴」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「咁你知唔知冇冧巴既係咩部門呀，因為我一直都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />回避問題「總之個d就係其他部門」（割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「依家知兩位呀sir唔係冒警，咁我都冇問題喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔知兩位貴姓呢」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死都唔肯講，話冧巴就係佢地身分<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢地都走喇，好似係我放佢地走咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n49159 李_榮<br />\n25968 無名小卒 柴都冇<br />\n<br />\n呢個故事教訓我地，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">見到狗就屌啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d8b617daa62108cec94c1a70844deadc31796d","tid":1481562,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:15:50.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n818維園見！所有聽日去嘅人都同我入一入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"81339a8834f753983836fc69190f389cccffea6f","tid":1481562,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:16:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b78d69a8604e847e5bb03ae450cbf37a4b49aa71","tid":1481562,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e2929da8a7b73862d254f018bbbe901aa6335d","tid":1481562,"uid":177732,"like":134,"dislike":0,"score":134,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:25:28.000Z","msg":"平時d popo入去d高級住宅做野比人撚得仲勁<br />\n一黎就你份糧我地出 架下叫你做小小野有咩問題<br />\n入到去d popo 個頭全程望住地下"},{"pid":"d924509c03f835e71b7e1c69cbe1e3c1f19e3103","tid":1481562,"uid":92908,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"21e2929da8a7b73862d254f018bbbe901aa6335d","tid":1481562,"uid":177732,"like":134,"dislike":0,"score":134,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:25:28.000Z","msg":"平時d popo入去d高級住宅做野比人撚得仲勁<br />\n一黎就你份糧我地出 架下叫你做小小野有咩問題<br />\n入到去d popo 個頭全程望住地下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />窮撚，未見識過"},{"pid":"2e8cb6d0b8cf7e1b118f8af239eafa90ea4396b0","tid":1481562,"uid":225455,"like":110,"dislike":5,"score":105,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:27:28.000Z","msg":"咁係你遇著好狗姐<br />\n講真有更多既係見你串撚77就拉撚左你啦<br />\n原因就唔洗我講啦<br />\n是但作話你阻差辦公咁"},{"pid":"79389c354191e27f530365a02b1cfdd9a5e28315","tid":1481562,"uid":92908,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2e8cb6d0b8cf7e1b118f8af239eafa90ea4396b0","tid":1481562,"uid":225455,"like":110,"dislike":5,"score":105,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:27:28.000Z","msg":"咁係你遇著好狗姐<br />\n講真有更多既係見你串撚77就拉撚左你啦<br />\n原因就唔洗我講啦<br />\n是但作話你阻差辦公咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"隻狗都有咁講，話阻差辦公"},{"pid":"73dae9aebaa7e8ec8bf3299e671bfaec1e070b6c","tid":1481562,"uid":121610,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:31:24.000Z","msg":"拉返去要寫report wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468bffc906f9e982150f5db942f8bbbd7bf6ada3","tid":1481562,"uid":177732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"73dae9aebaa7e8ec8bf3299e671bfaec1e070b6c","tid":1481562,"uid":121610,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:31:24.000Z","msg":"拉返去要寫report wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:32:18.000Z","msg":"要開檔案做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6288afa0594d77203da7ce15b1d96a56824d1f9","tid":1481562,"uid":92908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:32:20.000Z","msg":"每次見到狗就好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31018d7c79808cc2d4717d042104ec39bd96344f","tid":1481562,"uid":268251,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:32:48.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNrEn9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNrEn9y.jpg&h=3a63f7b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1481244/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1481244/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原圖既少女, 係孤星淚入面既Cosette. 孤星淚係咩故事, 大家應該都知, 唔知自己google.<br />\n留意左好多文日, 我地既文宣其實可以利用唔同地方既文化,<br />\n加以更改, 達成更大效果. 要同全世界We Connect, 要活用唔同地方既文化.<br />\n孤星淚, 係歐美社會一定知道既title, 亦容易勾起佢地既共鳴.<br />\n大家不妨諗諗之後既文宣, 要更加creative.<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手forward去外國網站或者FB,<br />\n喺澳洲同法國既香港支持者受到大陸人攻擊之下,<br />\n呢張圖就係我地對外文宣既最佳利器.<br />\n當年南斯拉夫內戰, 打左幾年, 國際社會關注但唔出手,<br />\n最後係一張『薩拉熱窩的羅密歐與茱麗葉』既照片成為轉變關鍵.<br />\n羅密歐與茱麗葉既標題, 引起左歐美社會共鳴.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 發夢之歌: 自由之旗・自由之民, 一首代表我地理念既歌.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1476260/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1476260/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我地唔單止要宣傳, 仲要有理念. 追求自由係最好既理念,<br />\n唔會嚇親老一派既香港人, 亦可以觸動到歐美社會既支持.<br />\n我選呢首歌既理由, 同上面講既『薩拉熱窩的羅密歐與茱麗葉』一樣,<br />\n都係能觸動歐美普世價值既issue. 對我地黎講, 一首好歌,<br />\n可以鼓舞士氣, 提醒我地不要放棄.<br />\n<br />\n上面條LINK係我搵既一首歌, 好適合我地用. 大家可以襟上去聽下首歌,<br />\n如果認同既話, 我希望可以搞個萬人齊唱版, 大家可以聽住音樂清唱,<br />\n唱完之後UPLOAD上上面條LINK, 我整合之後放出黎.<br />\n<br />\n文宣也好, 歌曲也好, 最重要係做得到be Symbol.<br />\nBatman曾有一段對話:<br />\n&ldquo;People need dramatic examples to shake them out of apathy,<br />\nand I can&rsquo;t do that as Bruce Wayne. As a man I&rsquo;m flesh and blood,<br />\nI can be ignored, I can be destroyed, but as a symbol,<br />\nas a symbol I can be incorruptible. I can be everlasting.&rdquo;<br />\n&mdash; Bruce Wayne (Batman Begins)<br />\n<br />\n我地既文宣同理念, 一定要做到be Symbol, 能有代表性, 見到某D文宣圖就諗起成個運動,<br />\n聽到某首歌就能夠代表我地並能觸動人心. 一切既品牌, 都係Symbol. 國旗係Symbol,<br />\n明星效應係Symbol. be Symbol, be Symbol, be Symbol. 重要事情講三次.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n818，維園見"},{"pid":"e50f6a4657742d840d50069a88ce42adab5755d2","tid":1481562,"uid":89514,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:33:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8465efa11e23c2808823753669b872d71236819","tid":1481562,"uid":92908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e50f6a4657742d840d50069a88ce42adab5755d2","tid":148